homepage":"","overview":"新当老师的陈侠（甄子丹饰），一入职便遇上学校杀校危机，又要面对一众品学皆劣的问题学生，包括好勇斗狠的伟聪（骆明劼饰）、印巴籍祖发（刘朝健饰）、男人头得男（李靖筠饰）、专注力不足的启程（汤君慈饰）及只会打游戏机的启贤（汤君耀饰）。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Henry Chen (Donnie Yen) seorang guru yang memilki metode pengajaran tidak biasa sangat dekat dengan murid-muridnya. Dia bukanlah guru biasa karena dia dapat melakukan apapun demi menjaga murid-muridnya. Suatu ketika salah satu muridnya disekap oleh geng penjahat, hal ini membuat dia melakukan perlawanan untuk mendapatkan muridnya kembali."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un maestro que se convierte en soldado en la escuela secundaria usa métodos inusuales para llegar a una clase de estudiantes pobres al tratar con un empresario codicioso y su pandilla de luchadores, así como con el gobierno."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"大師兄","runtime":101,"tagline":"讀書不是為了考試 而是為了改變人生","homepage":"","overview":"現在教書也很危險！黑道找小弟，奸商搶校地，老師該如何自處？\r 數學老師也可以是武術冠軍，地表最強老師的另類春風化雨，看他如何收服問題學生。  新老師陳俠（甄子丹飾）一上任就發現學校有廢校危機，又接手了一班問題學生，他運用了獨特的教學方式，讓學生各各有了轉變。一切看似漸入佳境，卻發生了意外，陳俠成了眾矢之的，面臨失去教職的危機；同時，又有違法商人介入學校土地買賣，讓校園不得安寧，讓師生決定合力來場校園保衛戰！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Da shi xiong","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Na střední školu Tak Čch' nastupuje s novým školním rokem učitel Henry Čchen. Je to bývalý mariňák, který nemá s učením zatím žádné zkušenosti. Stane se třídním 6.B, kam chodí hodně problémových žáků, které učení zrovna moc nebere. Svým bezprostředním a svérázným přístupem se snaží vzbudit nejen jejich zájem o studium, ale i zlepšit jejich domácí poměry."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"빅 브라더","runtime":100,"tagline":"지금까지 이런 형님은 없었다!","homepage":"","overview":"불량 학생들이 넘치는 F. 6B반의 담임 선생님 겸 일반 상식 선생님으로 들어간 ‘진협’(견자단)은 본인만의 방법으로 학생들과 가까워지려 노력하고, 그에게 학생들은 점점 마음의 문을 열게 된다. 학생들 한 명 한 명의 속사정을 알아가고, 위험에 처한 학생을 구하려던 중 진협은 패싸움에 휘말리게 되면서 학교에서 퇴출당할 위기에 놓이게 되는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Dai si hing","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Големият брат","runtime":101,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Войник преквалифицирал се в учител, използва необичайни методи спрямо клас от бедни ученици. В същото време той има проблеми с алчен предприемач и неговата банда бойци, както и с правителството."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Big Brother","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Um soldado que virou professor do ensino médio usa métodos incomuns para alcançar uma classe de estudantes pobres, enquanto lida com um empreendedor ganancioso e sua gangue de combatentes, bem como o governo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Большой брат","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Мистер Чэн приходит устраиваться учителем в обычную гонконгскую школу. Учебное заведение находится на грани закрытия, так как поступаемость в вузы у её выпускников почти нулевая. Но мистер Чэн, обладающий полезными знаниями, эффективными умениями и необычными методами преподавания, начинает бороться с неуспеваемостью и хромающей дисциплиной в классе."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Askeri Öğretmen Olursa","homepage":"","overview":"Henry Chen Xia, askeri liseden mezun olduktan sonra hayatına bu yönde devam eden okulda eğitim vermek üzere görevlendirilir. Bu görevinde öğrenciler ile disiplinli bir ilişki kuran Chen Xia, öğrencilere kaldıramayacaklarından fazla yükleme yapmaya çalışınca garip görüntüler ortaya çıkar. Chen Xia, bu okulda hem öğrencilere eğitim verip hemde bazı çeteler ile mücadele etmektedir. Aç gözlü bir girişimcinin yaptıklarına karşıda kayıtsız kalamayan Chen Xia bir yandan da onunla uğraşmak zorunda kalacaktır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Big Brother","runtime":102,"tagline":"Grand frère","homepage":"","overview":"Un soldat devenu professeur de lycée utilise des méthodes inhabituelles pour atteindre une classe d'élèves pauvres, tout en traitant avec un entrepreneur cupide et sa bande de combattants ainsi qu'avec le gouvernement."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Đại Sư Huynh","runtime":120,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Một giáo viên trung học mỗi ngày đều đặn tới trường gõ đầu trẻ cho đến một hôm…cậu học sinh do anh chủ nhiệm dính vào rắc rối với một băng đảng xã hội đen và bị bắt cóc. Đó cũng là lúc bí mật của“anh” thầy trước giờ luôn hiền lành, hết mực yêu thương học sinh và có tâm với nghề bị bộc lộ. Có vẻ như quá khứ máu lửa không buông tha “anh” thầy mà buộc anh phải trở lại con người xưa nhưng có khác là lần này không phải chiến đấu cho bản thân anh, mà cho những đứa trẻ mà anh luôn xem chúng như những đứa em trai."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ένας στρατιώτης προσλαμβάνετε σαν δάσκαλος σε ένα γυμνάσιο και χρησιμοποιεί ασυνήθιστες μεθόδους για να διδάξει σε μια τάξη φτωχών μαθητών, ενώ ασχολείται και με έναν άπληστο επιχειρηματία και τη συμμορία των μαχητών του καθώς και την κυβέρνηση."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"スーパーティーチャー 熱血格闘","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Big Brother","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Big Brother opowiada historię byłego żołnierza, który zostaje nauczycielem w liceum. W czasie poszukiwań jednego z uczniów mężczyzna wchodzi w konflikt z chciwym przedsiębiorcą, wojownikami MMA oraz z rządem."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Big Brother","runtime":111,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un soldado convertido en profesor de secundaria utiliza métodos inusuales para llegar a una clase de estudiantes pobres, mientras trata con un empresario codicioso y su banda de combatientes, así como con el gobierno."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Великий брат","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Непростий шкільний учитель має корисні вміння, і, як водиться в таких випадках, темним минулим на додачу. У пошуках зниклого учня він зіткнеться зі злочинною бандою."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ทหารที่ผันตัวมาเป็นครูโรงเรียนมัธยมใช้วิธีการที่ไม่ธรรมดาเพื่อเข้าถึงนักเรียนกลุ่มหนึ่งที่ยากจน ขณะเดียวกันก็ต้องจัดการกับผู้ประกอบการที่โลภมากและกลุ่มนักรบของเขา รวมถึงรัฐบาล"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Didysis brolis","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Drąsus karys, tapęs vidurinės mokyklos mokytoju, taiko netradicinius metodus, kad įkvėptų ir pasiektų vargstančių mokinių klasę, tuo pat metu grumdamasis su gobšaus verslininko ir jo kovotojų gaujos keliamais pavojais bei vyriausybės spaudimu. Ši įkvepianti istorija atskleidžia mokymo iššūkius ir kovą už teisingumą, pabrėždama atsidavimą bei drąsą prieš neteisybę."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":141715,"adult":false,"title":"Big Boobs Buster","video":false,"overview":"Another buxom bombshell falls prey to the masked vigilante, the Big Boobs Buster! Rumor has it that the vengeful villainess was once a mild mannered student ridiculed and rejected for her small bust size. Now, the spurned woman gets even by donning a ridiculous costume and taunting her well-endowed nemeses. Will bouncy coeds across the land be forced under cover? Is any bosomy beauty safe from the Big Boobs Buster?","genre_ids":[35,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0866,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/tRRS3dC3ugPzKEVud5tcXTW9Prk.jpg","release_date":"1990-04-25","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/1uxIX7sCkmMYxszELWAHJcLWRyN.jpg","original_title":"巨乳ハンター","original_language":"ja"},{"id":522921,"adult":false,"title":"How Long Will I Love U","video":false,"overview":"Gu Xiaojiao, a young girl from 2018 and Lu Ming, a man from 1999, discover that they have both woken up in the same bed at the same space-time. More surprisingly, they realize that they can time travel by exiting the bedroom door. The fun begins when they start to plan a number of changes within these two eras. However, they do not know that their destiny is in the hands of a mysterious person.","genre_ids":[35,10749,18,9648,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5883,"vote_count":52,"poster_path":"/ud0N7ot24votfoMAu6BxjPGXqOV.jpg","release_date":"2018-05-18","vote_average":6.635,"backdrop_path":"/qHC2eMB57aXcY8JHDhWsC25NZ0e.jpg","original_title":"超时空同居","original_language":"zh"},{"id":411442,"adult":false,"title":"Time Raiders","video":false,"overview":"Time Raiders is based on the online novel series Daomu Biji written by Xu Lei.  It tells the story of explorers searching for the secrets of immortality in ancient tombs","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8082,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/qtbJL3pWPJIO8KGqZpRLEn4jmQp.jpg","release_date":"2016-08-18","vote_average":5.296,"backdrop_path":"/96SopW64ZEipVXtPzHb3pOERtWu.jpg","original_title":"盗墓笔记","original_language":"zh"},{"id":505568,"adult":false,"title":"A Beautiful Moment","video":false,"overview":"An ageing bachelor playboy finally meets the girl of his dreams and proposes marriage, only to discover her psychologist stepmom was his first love long ago. The future in-laws initially pretend not to know each other but as the wedding date gets nearer, the rekindling of long-dormant feelings develops into a cross-generational love triangle.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.479,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/yYeZhWBcWD8jNzQl0mXg7INYhA7.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-15","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/zX4GubAp1npfgckNDPxfpsNkBHQ.jpg","original_title":"我的情敵女婿","original_language":"cn"},{"id":319832,"adult":false,"title":"Guna 369","video":false,"overview":"Guna is a happy-go-lucky guy who believes the solution to solving issues is not through violence but through compromise.When he is framed for a crime he didn't commit by someone close to him, Guna is left with no choice and forced to the extremes to prove his innocence.","genre_ids":[10749,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2641,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/1LuEpIbLDbKOJT1CpfhhXTnIK8T.jpg","release_date":"2019-08-02","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/kiXaBWKPez08PrUshRcsvvkSAd2.jpg","original_title":"గుణ 369","original_language":"te"},{"id":481899,"adult":false,"title":"Corpse Prison: Part 2","video":false,"overview":"They thought they were coming to study a mysterious town hidden in the mountains of Japan. Instead, they’ve discovered that their Professor brought them to Yasaka for a much darker purpose. Now Mikoto and the other girls are trapped in a monstrous nightmare. As the villagers become increasingly more insane, the college students find themselves at the center of arcane rituals focused on blood and rotting flesh. Their only chance is to escape, but their captors are far too numerous and know the lay of the local land far too well.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8457,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/bAUjXSpnizDkSg4qa08PWuesrVV.jpg","release_date":"2017-06-10","vote_average":6.222,"backdrop_path":"/vLGFd5s72tdmokwKRiKhwFHO9UC.jpg","original_title":"劇場版 屍囚獄 結ノ篇","original_language":"ja"},{"id":413198,"adult":false,"title":"Call of Heroes","video":false,"overview":"During the warlords era in China, a village located in rural area called Pucheng fell into dangerous situation when its government allocated all its military force to the front line, the cruel commandant Cao from the enemy troops arrived the village and killed the innocent, the guardians of Pucheng were desperate to fight against Cao for justice and to protect their homeland.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0064,"vote_count":97,"poster_path":"/frNzgqcLNno44PhcNREjM7AEXWL.jpg","release_date":"2016-08-12","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/fugdTm2XsAIxT5wVfp20lfogJak.jpg","original_title":"危城","original_language":"cn"},{"id":872177,"adult":false,"title":"Corrective Measures","video":false,"overview":"Set in San Tiburon, the world's most dangerous maximum-security penitentiary and home to the world's most treacherous superpowered criminals, where tensions among the inmates and staff heighten, leading to anarchy that engulfs the prison and order is turned upside down.","genre_ids":[878,28,53,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7296,"vote_count":107,"poster_path":"/aHFq9NMhavOL0jtQvmHQ1c5e0ya.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-29","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/i6u0xPuFLAxdELBxUit75fyBqlq.jpg","original_title":"Corrective Measures","original_language":"en"},{"id":575219,"adult":false,"title":"Pegasus","video":false,"overview":"Zhang Chi, a hubris and dominating six-time racing champion, falls from grace following a crisis. After a five-year suspension from the motorsport, the now single-father to a six-year-old boy throws down the gauntlet once again.","genre_ids":[35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.123,"vote_count":106,"poster_path":"/tPqtna4fStMA61KiWUYaeAjf22c.jpg","release_date":"2019-02-05","vote_average":6.594,"backdrop_path":"/smCOdLvDR54fDRStUXnxZrP9I7B.jpg","original_title":"飞驰人生","original_language":"zh"},{"id":455043,"adult":false,"title":"God of War","video":false,"overview":"During the 16th century, pirates rule the Chinese coastline, pillaging the small villages and terrorizing the citizens. When maverick leader Commander Yu enlists the help of a sharp young general, they devise a plan to defeat the pirates. A violent clash of wit and weapons will decide who will rule the land.","genre_ids":[28,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5428,"vote_count":99,"poster_path":"/4rWq9Vwb1gVhQIqkhUKE0hPVwnz.jpg","release_date":"2017-05-27","vote_average":6.359,"backdrop_path":"/XrpxJywc12kjV5PQPFgpmJTRpY.jpg","original_title":"荡寇风云","original_language":"zh"},{"id":267467,"adult":false,"title":"The Target","video":false,"overview":"At the same time as murder suspect Yeo-hoon is brought unconscious to the emergency room following a shooting incident, an assailant breaks into the house of Tae-jun, the emergency room's doctor in charge, and kidnaps his wife. The kidnapper calls the doctor and tells him to bring Yeo-hoon to him. To retrieve his wife, Tae-jun has no option but to save the patient and sneak him away before the police can notice.","genre_ids":[53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.827,"vote_count":130,"poster_path":"/rbYb65lmQgDPzd2VuC8QoF8wPQZ.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-30","vote_average":7.008,"backdrop_path":"/oquMboQfqtfFMNW9SSHpm0EVGHU.jpg","original_title":"표적","original_language":"ko"},{"id":18331,"adult":false,"title":"The Nutty Professor","video":false,"overview":"A timid, nearsighted chemistry teacher discovers a magical potion that can transform him into a suave and handsome Romeo. The Jekyll and Hyde game works well enough until the concoction starts to wear off at the most embarrassing times.","genre_ids":[35,878,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5654,"vote_count":457,"poster_path":"/a3lzU19j7WGfyXVDfPMdh8DAkru.jpg","release_date":"1963-06-04","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/kTgPUrv6jICp5CDDq5vS40zvVKX.jpg","original_title":"The Nutty Professor","original_language":"en"},{"id":20329,"adult":false,"title":"Death Note: L Change the WorLd","video":false,"overview":"\"The human whose name is written in the Death Note shall die.\" After making the hardest decision ever, another serious case confronts L. There are only 23 days left and without his best partner Watari, L has to solve the case all by himself for the very first time.","genre_ids":[14,28,53,878,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4205,"vote_count":298,"poster_path":"/sxtU5dLduyjO8Jii9wdfYq2MK9f.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-07","vote_average":6.025,"backdrop_path":"/m4qM1XvABr1mVKWKohvHA7obLsY.jpg","original_title":"L change the WorLd","original_language":"ja"},{"id":13127,"adult":false,"title":"SPL: Kill Zone","video":false,"overview":"Chan, an articulate senior detective nearing the end of his career, is taking care of the daughter of a witness killed by ruthless crime lord Po. Martial arts expert Ma is set to take over as head of the crime unit, replacing Chan who wants an early retirement.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8454,"vote_count":349,"poster_path":"/38xh96dcfj6Z3aDj5phYZwKwHDn.jpg","release_date":"2005-11-18","vote_average":6.937,"backdrop_path":"/7uJmhgeKWYEGp4UydW9NhsOEhYP.jpg","original_title":"殺破狼","original_language":"cn"},{"id":795853,"adult":false,"title":"Gaia","video":false,"overview":"In the depths of an ancient forest, something has been growing. Something older than humanity itself, and perhaps greater too. When a park ranger discovers a man and his son living wild, she stumbles onto a secret that is about to change the world.","genre_ids":[27,14,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9585,"vote_count":229,"poster_path":"/v8cwfPwjHDWf5s5MxvLvcfnxPLL.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-18","vote_average":5.919,"backdrop_path":"/hm8gTyliPMvcC9ikt0njV18cS3Q.jpg","original_title":"Gaia","original_language":"en"},{"id":601165,"adult":false,"title":"Legacy of Lies","video":false,"overview":"An ex-MI6 agent is thrown back into the world of espionage and high stakes to uncover the shocking truth about operations conducted by unknown secret services.","genre_ids":[53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8606,"vote_count":249,"poster_path":"/bhNHCeJDFDaB00A46AoCw2mggdE.jpg","release_date":"2020-07-28","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/nxxODhq9I05Ze9uLONGvfDrzaUO.jpg","original_title":"Legacy of Lies","original_language":"en"},{"id":9750,"adult":false,"title":"Balls of Fury","video":false,"overview":"Randy Daytona was a child ping pong prodigy who lost his chance at Olympic gold when his father is murdered by the mysterious Feng over a gambling debt. 15yrs later he's down on his luck and scraping a living doing seedy back room shows in Vegas; when the FBI turn up and ask for his help to take down Feng... who just happens to love Ping Pong.","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8721,"vote_count":584,"poster_path":"/1Uc6lFCcNlaKP5uLJdQAhdDfihy.jpg","release_date":"2007-08-29","vote_average":5.285,"backdrop_path":"/cUDzGeQ5d4LVDu8ma1z9U02fo3k.jpg","original_title":"Balls of Fury","original_language":"en"},{"id":13928,"adult":false,"title":"Knick Knack","video":false,"overview":"Life on a shelf as a snowman trapped in a snow-globe blizzard can become wearing, especially when you're surrounded by knickknacks from sunnier locales. When the jaded snowman finally breaks free of his glass house, his vacation plans are cut short.","genre_ids":[16,10751,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7545,"vote_count":600,"poster_path":"/ouk2QFv4NySNfitAgXqnTtO5vA1.jpg","release_date":"1989-11-23","vote_average":7.013,"backdrop_path":"/yTnQmpV4Ct0vy0WBUPsHvNIBWWq.jpg","original_title":"Knick Knack","original_language":"en"},{"id":85925,"adult":false,"title":"Tres lancheros muy picudos","video":false,"overview":"Son las emocionantes aventuras de tres lancheros holgazanes en Acapulco. Cada uno de ellos se ve involucrado en diferentes problemas y tienen que salir huyendo a la ciudad de México. Ahí se esconden en la casa de unas amigas para evadir a los gangsters que los buscan solo que las muchachas resultan ser prostitutas y todo se complica. The exciting adventures of three men who drive boats in Acapulco. Each gets involved in different problems and all have to run away to Mexico City to elude the gangsters who are after them. They hide in the house of some lady friends who turn out to be \"working girls\" and things get really wild.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4422,"vote_count":138,"poster_path":"/DNTQYQUgXJPtWDKe186uqIGJhL.jpg","release_date":"1989-08-17","vote_average":7.62,"backdrop_path":"/saLrMdXK0EWKIwt85DMlyJN3P8U.jpg","original_title":"Tres lancheros muy picudos","original_language":"es"},{"id":394374,"adult":false,"title":"At the End of the Tunnel","video":false,"overview":"A paraplegic computer engineer that moves in a wheelchair and works in his basement starts hearing noises and voices of bank-robbers.","genre_ids":[80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2571,"vote_count":439,"poster_path":"/gKfm5UqRwvoNiImFQLEH2WDMK5S.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-21","vote_average":7.044,"backdrop_path":"/wsD8nxCRrVyGLsBLQhVgtTdl6Kr.jpg","original_title":"Al final del túnel","original_language":"es"}],"similar_content":[],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt7336572","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q56272751","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":100837,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_recep